apollo.dataadapter.das
Interface DASSequence

All Known Implementing Classes:
SimpleDASSequence
public interface DASSequence

I represent the data contained in a dna sequence (as defined by the DAS-spec) needed by Apollo to display a sequence. I have a reference implementation in the simple sub-package
